org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Dependability.ThreatsPropagation

Interface Attack

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, InternalPropagation, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AttackImpl

    public interface Attack
extends InternalPropagation
    A representation of the model object 'Attack'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Kind
    • Severity
    • Likelihood
    • Vulnerability
    • Threat
    • Base Message
    • Intensity
    See Also:
    ThreatsPropagationPackage.getAttack()
